<div class="container-big">

  <div class="section-one">
    <div class="big-yellow-square"></div>
    <div class="cta">
      <h1>Mentorship is the key to our success</h1>
      <h6 class="mt-50">We help women come together to learn from each other and achieve their goals, because women can be a powerful force for change in the world.</h6>
      <div class="landing-buttons">
        <%= link_to root_path do %>
          <p class="btn btn-solid">Start Now</p>
        <% end %>
        <%= link_to root_path do %>
          <p class="btn btn-ghost">See mentors</p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="landing-image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554200876-56c2f25224fa?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80" alt="two women laughing" width=720>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-two">
    <div class="header d-flex align-items-center">
      <h2 class="text-align-center mx-auto">Why mentorship?</h2>
    </div>

    <div id="carouselExampleControls-a" class="carousel slide" data-interval="false">
      <div class="carousel-inner carousel-container">

        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <div class="section-two-images-and-text d-flex justify-space-around align-items-center">
            <div class="image-collage">
              <div class="image-2">
               <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508214751196-bcfd4ca60f91?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="photo of woman2">
              </div>
              <div class="image-3">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1477118476589-bff2c5c4cfbb?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="photo of woman3">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-two-text">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path('left-quote (1).png')) %>
              <h6 class="px-4">When I wanted to change industry and look for a job, for example, my mentor jumped in to help with interview prep and to make introductions.”</h6>
              <p class="px-4">-Alberta Lowe</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <div class="section-two-images-and-text d-flex justify-space-around align-items-center">
            <div class="image-collage">
              <div class="image-1">
               <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526080652727-5b77f74eacd2?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1510&q=80" alt="photo of woman2">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-two-text">
              <%= image_tag(asset_path('left-quote (1).png')) %>
              <h6 class="px-4">I’m such an introvert, but talking to my mentor has made things totally different for me. It has definitely helped build my confidence. Now I can actually say that I’m a leader.”</h6>
              <p class="px-4">-Lisa Chinn</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="d-flex justify-content-start" href="#carouselExampleControls-a" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-button-left"><</span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="d-flex justify-content-end" href="#carouselExampleControls-a" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-button-right">></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-three">

    <div class="header-three">
      <h2>How Ellevate Works</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="header-paragraph-three">
       <p>We provide all the materials you need - including skill-building videos, discussion guides, and worksheets on topics from negotiating your salary to discovering your strengths. #LetsEllevateEachOther</p>
    </div>

    <div class="how-ellevate-works-info">
      <div class="icon-and-info">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path('coffee.png')) %>
        <h6>Our Matching Algorithm</h6>
        <p>Our matching algorithm works to match you with the best possible mentor for your needs. Blah blah blah blah blah</p>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-and-info">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path('calendar.png')) %>
        <h6>Regular Meetings</h6>
        <p>Meet with your mentor at least bi-weekly for three months. Research supports that this amount of regularity works best.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-and-info">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path('save (2).png')) %>
        <h6>Mentors are everywhere.</h6>
        <p>We’re a community of women who meet in nearly every country and at some of the largest companies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-and-info">
        <%= image_tag(asset_path('bar-chart.png')) %>
        <h6>Mentorship Works</h6>
        <p>86% of women in Circles say their group has made a positive impact on their life. Blah blah blah blah blah blah.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="how-ellevate-works-video-and-steps">
      <div class="ellevate-video">
        <iframe width="550" height="400" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/R1qVPWEleRY">
        </iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="ellevate-steps">
        <h5>Getting started is easy</h5>

        <div class="all-steps">
          <div class="card-step">
            <div class="step-number">
              <p>Step 1:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <h4>Take the Survey</h4>
              <p>We recommend small groups of 8 to 12 women—but many Circles start off with even fewer members.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-step">
            <div class="step-number">
              <p>Step 2:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <h4>Get Matched Immediately</h4>
              <p>Circles can meet anywhere—at work, home, a nearby coffee shop, or online.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-step">
            <div class="step-number">
              <p>Step 3:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <h4>Choose a Mentor</h4>
              <p>Choose from dozens of meeting guides on topics from networking to negotiating.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-step">
            <div class="step-number">
              <p>Step 4:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-text">
              <h4>Send a message to your mentor</h4>
              <p>We recommend small groups of 8 to 12 women—but many Circles start off with even fewer members.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="steps-button">
          <%= link_to "Take the Survey", root_path, class: "btn-solid"%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-four">
    <div>
      <div class="header-four">
        <h2>Our Mentors</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mentors">
      <% @mentors = User.select { |user| !user.mentee } %>
        <% @mentors.sample(3).each do |mentor| %>
          <%= link_to profile_path(mentor), target: "_blank" do %>
          <div class="col-4 my-2">
            <div class="mentor-card-container">
              <div class="mentor-card">
                <%= cl_image_tag mentor.photo  %>
                <h6><%= mentor.first_name %> <%= mentor.last_name %></h6>
                <p><%= mentor.profile.current_title %> at <%= mentor.profile.current_employer %></p>
                <p><%= mentor.profile.city %>, <%= mentor.profile.state %></p>
              </div>
              <div class="mentor-tagline">
                <p>"<%= mentor.profile.tagline %>"</p>
              </div>
              <div class="match-button">
                <%= link_to "View Profile", profile_path(mentor), class: "btn-solid small"%>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-five">

    <div>
      <div class="header-five">
        <h2>Join the Ellevate Community</h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="community">

      <div class="com-card-and-button">
        <div class="community-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531058020387-3be344556be6?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80)">
          EVENTS
        </div>
        <div class="comm-card-button">
          <%= link_to "See All Events", root_path, class: "btn-ghost-solid"%>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="com-card-and-button">
        <div class="community-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1491975474562-1f4e30bc9468?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=60)">
          FORUMS
        </div>
        <div class="comm-card-button">
          <%= link_to "See All Forums", root_path, class: "btn-ghost-solid"%>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="com-card-and-button">
        <div class="community-card" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556565681-306458ef93cd?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80)">
          WORKSHOPS
        </div>
        <div class="comm-card-button">
          <%= link_to "See All Workshops", root_path, class: "btn-ghost-solid"%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>












